### Buderus Controller (internal Web API)
### Base URL is the Haus application server

@baseUrl = {{$dotenv HAUS_BASE_URL}}

### Get current snapshot
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/buderus
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get all cached values
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/buderus/values
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get cached values by datapoint id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/buderus/dhwCircuits
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Set a datapoint value
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/buderus/heatingCircuits/hc1/temperatureRoomSetpoint
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": 21.0
}
